This document is only issued to employers participating in the Home Office’s pilot for authenticating the biometric residence permit of an employee, or prospective employee, in their organisation. 

Employers must not treat this document as authentic unless it has been received:
as a result of that employer reading a biometric residence permit with the express permission of the holder of the permit; and
as a consequence of that employer’s registered participation in the pilot. 

You may wish to retain this document for your records. 
